## Quick Reference

| Phase | Question Answered | Key Output |
|-------|-------------------|------------|
| 1. Budget | "How fast should each part be?" | Budget allocation table |
| 2. Causal | "What's the root cause that matters most?" | Bottleneck ranking + causal graph |
| 3. Narrative | "What does the request actually experience?" | Before/After journey story |
| âڈ³ Debt | "When will this break in production?" | Time-to-Incident forecast |
| ًں‘» Ghost | "What work is done but never used?" | Waste ratio per data source |
| ًں’£ Blast | "Who feels it if this degrades?" | Impact surface map |
| ًں•³ï¸ڈ Leak | "Does it get slower the longer it runs?" | Gradual degradation patterns |
| ًں“گ Entropy | "How predictable is the response time?" | Entropy-latency landscape |

| Signal | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| One layer > 150% of budget | ًں”´ Critical overrun â€” must fix |
| One layer 110-150% of budget | ًںں، Warning â€” requires optimization |
| Causal graph has node with out-degree â‰¥ 3 | ًں”‘ High-leverage bottleneck |
| Leverage score > 70 | Fix this first, regardless of severity |
| Health score < 60 | Systemic performance issue |
| FIXED layer over budget | May need infra/arch change (not just code) |
| TTI < 1 month | ًں”´ Imminent incident â€” fix now |
| Ghost waste > 50ms/req | ًں”´ Significant wasted computation |
| Blast Radius > 70 | ًں”´ Company-level risk if this degrades |
| Time leak with no reset mechanism | ًں”´ Will degrade until next restart |
| Entropy H > 1.5 (high latency) | ًں”´ Worst user experience â€” slow + unpredictable |

