### Quality Check (Rules 1-7)
- [ ] **Rule 1 â€” Concrete Fixes:** Every P0/P1 fix includes runnable code in the same language as the reviewed code? (NOT "use a JOIN" â€” show the JOIN)
- [ ] **Rule 2 â€” Confidence Labels:** Every time estimate annotated with (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW confidence)? Search for any bare number followed by "ms" without a confidence label.
