- [ ] **Rule 7 â€” Execution Plan:** âڈ±ï¸ڈ table present with 5-min/1-hour/1-day tiers, cumulative health scores, and dependency notes?
- [ ] **Continuous Learning:** `references/vulnerability-library.md` consulted before diagnosis? New patterns contributed after diagnosis (if any found)?
- [ ] **Vulnerability Scan:** 8-type vulnerability detection executed? ًں”’ section present if any found; explicitly omitted if none?
